$ drivers/hv

The `drivers/hv` directory contains → Windows/optional-features/Hyper-V#hyper-v-linux-src[Hyper-V related code] (such as the VMBus).

The → Windows/Subsystem-for-Linux modifications on the kernel include the subdirectory → Linux/kernel/source/drivers/hv/dxgkrnl[`dxgkrnl`] which is not present in Linus Torvald's repository.
